---
title: Booking Flow — Microservices
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant TG as Telegram
    participant GW as bot-gateway
    participant BK as booking-service
    participant PAY as payment-service
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant NOT as notification-service

    User->>TG: /book
    TG->>GW: update: message /book
    GW->>BK: GET /locations
    BK-->>GW: locations[]
    GW->>TG: sendMessage(locations + keyboard)

    User->>TG: click location
    TG->>GW: callback location:patriarchy
    GW->>BK: GET /resources?locationId=patriarchy
    BK-->>GW: resources[]
    GW->>TG: editMessage(resources + keyboard)

    User->>TG: click resource
    TG->>GW: callback resource:patriarchy:r1
    GW->>BK: GET /slots?resourceId=r1
    BK-->>GW: slots[]
    GW->>TG: editMessage(slots + keyboard)

    User->>TG: click slot
    TG->>GW: callback slot:r1:r1m
    GW->>BK: GET /resources/r1
    BK-->>GW: resource
    GW->>TG: editMessage(confirm booking prompt)

    User->>TG: click "Pay and book"
    TG->>GW: callback confirm:r1:r1m
    GW->>PAY: POST /invoices {chatId, resourceId, slotId}
    PAY->>REDIS: publish notification.send (send_invoice)
    REDIS->>NOT: consume send_invoice event
    NOT->>TG: sendInvoice(YooKassa)
    GW->>TG: editMessage("Invoice sent")

    User->>TG: pays invoice
    TG->>GW: pre_checkout_query
    GW->>PAY: POST /pre-checkout
    PAY-->>GW: {ok: true}
    GW->>TG: answerPreCheckoutQuery ok

    User->>TG: confirms payment
    TG->>GW: message.successful_payment
    GW->>PAY: POST /successful-payment
    PAY->>REDIS: publish payment.completed
    REDIS->>PAY: consume payment.completed
    PAY->>BK: POST /bookings
    BK-->>PAY: booking created
    BK->>REDIS: publish booking.created
    PAY->>REDIS: publish notification.send (booking confirmed)
    REDIS->>NOT: consume
    NOT->>TG: sendMessage("Booking confirmed")
